Phone Numbers in Offenbach am Main of Germany

Telobal provides Phone Number (Also known as Virtual Number or Direct Inward Dialing : DID) access numbers (sometimes referred to as virtual numbers) from Offenbach am Main, Germany (prefix: 49-69).

A local Offenbach am Main DID number may be forwarded by our infrastructure to Professional Virtual (Cloud-based) PBX, conventional PSTN (Plain Old Telephone System) devices, mobile phones or SIP anywhere in the world. The call forwarding destination is selected by the customer on a per-DID basis.

Virtual Number (DID) prices:

Setup price: 4.99 USD

Monthly price: 9.99 USD

Telobal offers an extensive selection of international DID numbers. In addition, we are constantly expanding our services so as to increase the number of regions supported, as well as to increase our coverage in each region.
